    public class MedicineListActivity
extends BaseAppCompatActivity
implements LoadJSONTask.Listener, android.widget.AdapterView.OnItemClickListener
    An activity to represent the medicine search/ list screen. This Activity is listed in the manifest as Searchable, meaning that search terms can be delivered here via calling onSearchRequested()
